Directed by Mikhil Musale

Written by Niren Bhatt. Parinda Joshi. Parinda Joshi. Mikhil Musale. Karan Vyas

Cast Rajkummar Rao (Raghuveer Mehta). Boman Irani (Dr. Tribhuvan Vardhi). Mouni Roy (Rukmini Mehta). Paresh Rawal (Tanmay Shah). Gajraj Rao (Abhay Chopra). Sumeet Vyas (Devraj Mehta). Manoj Joshi (Vitthalbhai Mehta). Sanjay Goradia (Natu Kaka). Amyra Dastur (Roopali). Amit Bimrot (Ravi). Chandan Bisht (Jagdish). Bijou Thaangjam (Chinese Official). Abhishek Banerjee (CBI Officer – AL Sharma). Chittaranjan Tripathy (CBI Officer – GS Gupta). Danni Wang(Xui Lee). Manvik Tanna (Chintoo Mehta). Sameer Kakkar (Raman Kaka (as Sameer Khakhar)). Shataf Figar (SIT Head). Jeffrey Ho (Hau Lee). Ragi Jani (Kahnuda). Sunita Shirole (Dhani Masi). Pranita Rajan (SIT Member #1). Aditi Khanna (SIT Member #2). Ramesh Murthy (SIT Member #3). Sheila Gore (SIT Member #4). Chien Ho Liao (Chinese Interpretor). Jayraj Freeman (Librarian (as Jay Jadeja)). Andrew Hoffland (Principal at Parent Meet). Hemang Dave (Parent Meet Organizer). Shahnaaz Deshpande (Chintoo’s School Principal). Chetan Daiya (I.J. Gohil (as Chetan Dhaiya)). Jay Bhatt (Sub-inspector BK Makwana). Gaurang Dhobi (Shady Sexologist #1). Manan Desai (Shady Sexologist #2). Bhargav Joshi (Bhide Bhai). Hiten Vasant (Bharat Bhai). Ojas Rawal (Jankrut). Ashmita Meghrajani (Patient #1). Sagar Shah (Patient #2). Rekha Mukherjee (Patient #3 (as Rekha Mukharjee)). Mehr Mahajan (TV Journalist (as Meher Mahajan)). Dawei Yu (General Zeng). Desiree Sangma (General Zeng’s Wife (as Desiree)). Pinky Parikh Desai (Cooking Show Host #1 (as Pinky Desai)). Pranali Mistry (Cooking Show Host #2). Shraddha Musale (Event Anchor). Chhavi Karnatak (Kayra). Chhaya Karnatak (Mayra). Kaw Ann Huang(Kha Lee – Chinese Official). Chang Shen Kao (Jo Hua – Chinese Official). Kishan Gadhvi (Chhagan (as Kishan Gadhavi)). Mehool Desai (School Peon (as Mehul Desai)) . Ruel Dausan Varandani (Choreographer (credit only)).Na Wang. David Yu (Chinese General)

Languages Hindi

Producers Sachin Agarwal. Sharada Karki. Sanjeev Mishra. Amit Singh. Dinesh Vijan

Production Maddock Film. Music-HrProductio. Skywalk Film
